        "meta_description": "“Youth retirement homes” have been popping up across China in recent years, promising a relaxing, communal experience away from the rigours of corporate and city life. Analysts suggest the trend is a sign of the times as young people face up to a stuttering economy, fiercely competitive job market and rising cos",
